eu.trentorise.opendata.traceprov.dcat

Class DcatCatalog.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.trentorise.opendata.traceprov.dcat.DcatCatalog.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    DcatCatalog

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class DcatCatalog.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of DcatCatalog. Initialize attributes and then invoke build() method to create immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread safe and generally should not be stored in field or collection, but used immediately to create instances.

      • from

        public final DcatCatalog.Builder from(DcatCatalog instance)
        Fill builder with attribute values from provided ADcatCatalog instance. Regular attribute values will be replaced with ones of an instance. Instance's absent optional values will not replace present values. Collection elements and entries will be added, not replaced.
        Parameters:
        instance - instance to copy values from
        Returns:
        this builder for chained invocation
